{"tid":1909567,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"1月9日，政府為《禁蒙面法》上訴，之後爆發武漢肺炎！","createTime":"2020-03-04T05:08:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T05:22:16.000Z","uid":14918,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c0328ec5b74000af963653c4231e9219497cfb2b","tid":1909567,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T05:08:47.000Z","msg":"請問法庭有判決未呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n梁天琦刑期上訴有判決未呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8993f2682a3f2d714817e09f356196367e227bad","tid":1909567,"uid":14918,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T05:10:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZftzSrr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZftzSrr.jpg&h=57565054&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fed04f4a263003ae8b09d9f9dfb2945ed3886513","tid":1909567,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T05:12:45.000Z","msg":"2020/01/09 16:05<br />\n無視武漢肺炎危機 港府執意上訴《禁蒙面法》<br />\n<br />\n李蘇竣 綜合報導  / 香港<br />\n<br />\n香港政府為了強硬壓制反送中抗爭群眾，日前頒布《緊急法》及《禁蒙面法》，但卻遭香港高等法院裁定違憲無效。港府不服提出上訴，今(9)日開庭審議，公民黨立法會議員郭榮鏗表示，武漢爆發肺炎，香港民眾陷入健康危機，呼籲港府「收手」。<br />\n<br />\n今(9)日於高等法院審理港府上訴案件，相關司法覆核申請人之一的公民黨立法會議員郭榮鏗，於開庭前向記者表示，《禁蒙面法》無助解決社會爭議，且現時武漢爆發肺炎，可能會出現公眾健康危機。他強調，市民目前正在四處搶購口罩，而政府卻針對《禁蒙面法》遭裁定違憲而提出上訴，他呼籲，政府應「馬上收手，不要一錯再錯」。"},{"pid":"f69c6f050080677648dac99e9d59c95d41bb718c","tid":1909567,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T05:19:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kpYj3AJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkpYj3AJ.png&h=b0eb2afd&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無法律界人士見過余若海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想知佢有無用口罩蒙面呀？"},{"pid":"6ae082e2b3faefb5e39fedbce0df20be53576b18","tid":1909567,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04